name: Dealbreaker
description:
🎲Cici is a nasty dealbreaker...🎲

🎲Dealbreaker is a horror game made in RPGMAKER VX ACE Where you play as a strange 13-year-old girl by the name of "Cici" while she bites off a bit more than she can chew as she jumps from one life to another. 🎲
🎲"When will she ever quit? It's been so long... So long... Since..."🎲

🎲There are three endings: Good, Bad, and the True end.🎲
🎲AVG. PLAYTIME: 20-25 MINS🎲
🎲This game is part of a series of games and does not include the full story of Cici.🎲

🎲This game is not suited for people faint of heart or sensitive to topics such as murder, suicide,  death, or dying.🎲

🎲Dealbreaker is made in collaboration with Walmartmadi.🎲
